      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">31.205-10</ph> Cost of money.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <ol id="d1940e13" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d1965e10" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">General</i>. Cost of money-</p>
               <ol id="d1940e26" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d1965e18" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
								                Is an imputed cost that is not a form of interest on borrowings (see <xref href="31.205-20.dita#FAR_31_205_20"
                              base="i1085239"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">31.205-20</xref>);</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d1965e26" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
								                Is an "incurred cost" for cost-reimbursement purposes under applicable cost-reimbursement contracts and for progress payment purposes under fixed-price contracts; and</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d1965e31" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
								                Refers to-</p>
                     <ol id="d1940e57" class="- topic/ol ">
                        <li class="- topic/li ">
                           <p id="d1965e37" class="- topic/p ">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(i)</ph>
										                    Facilities capital cost of money (48 CFR9904.414); and</p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="- topic/li ">
                           <p id="d1965e42" class="- topic/p ">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(ii)</ph>
										                    Cost of money as an element of the cost of capital assets under construction (48 CFR9904.417).</p>
                        </li>
                     </ol>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d1965e47" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
						            Cost of money is allowable, provided-</p>
               <ol id="d1940e89" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d1965e53" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
								                It is measured, assigned, and allocated to contracts in accordance with 48 CFR9904.414 or measured and added to the cost of capital assets under construction in accordance with 48 CFR9904.417, as applicable;</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d1965e58" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
								                The requirements of <xref href="31.205-52.dita#FAR_31_205_52"
                              base="i1085782"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">31.205-52</xref>, which limit the allowability of cost of money, are followed; and</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d1965e66" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
								                The estimated facilities capital cost of money is specifically identified and proposed in cost proposals relating to the contract under which the cost is to be claimed.</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d1965e71" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
						            Actual interest cost in lieu of the calculated imputed cost of money is unallowable.</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
